          "reviewBody": "Way of teaching and focus given to student' s  overall development is appreciative, highly qualified and co-operative teachers, positive environment where students are encouraged to achieve success and deal with their shortcomings.\nTeacher’s way of selection of topics from curriculum is commendable for keeping kids curious and excited so that they can explore more about topics of interest for self learning and regular update on Google classroom is boon for both parents and students.\nAppreciative dedication of teachers and their efforts in online classes is commendable.",
